						<div class="postbody">Yes you are right, it's good to be sure to not abuse a good idea you had. Asking to other people may not be that bad for sure, but when you write a game you often have to make choses that are hard to make, and you can't rely on other people to have an answer to all cases. It's really hard to make choises !
<br />
<br />Personally I didn't think thick or thin highlight made very much difference. But highlights are definitely much better than no highlights at all.</div>

					
